column14: SECOND LOOP TEST OR STATIONARY MB TEST SHOULD HAVE BEEN PERFORMED IF USER DID NOT BELIEVE FIRST LOOP TESTS RESULTS.  Stage steady through mmnt. DWL used as MGH. Loop indicated moving bed which shoud not occur as the channel is bed rock. The moving bed correction was not used.  Measurement was taken at the gauge and in a new spot since the RC boat was deployable at low stage. The mmnt indicated that a shift should be applied and looking at he curve there are no mmnts in this stage/discharge range. The lower end of the curve may need adjusting and a more thorough post processing of the mmnt in the office.    ADCP by Moving Boat
